window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>Fearful Rock and Other Precarious Locales</i> is the third volume of Night Shade Books' five volume \"Selected Stories of Manly Wade Wellman.\" This volume is made up of eight novella length stories. It includes Wellman's \"Judge Pursivant\" and \"Sergeant Jaeger\" stories, as well as a lost classic from <i>Strange Stories</i> (1939). In addition, it features an introduction by Wellman's long time friend, Stephen Jones, who provides a heartwarming bit of historical perspective on Wellman, and the influential shadow that his work as cast over the genre. Contents: </p><p></p><ul><li>Introduction by Stephen Jones </li><li>Fearful Rock </li><li>Coven </li><li>Toad's Foot </li><li>For the Love of a Witch </li><li>The Hairy Ones Shall Dance </li><li>The Black Drama </li><li>The Dreadful Rabbits </li><li>The Half-Haunted </li><li>Some Notes on the Texts by John Pelan</li></ul><p></p>"; 
